					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-707543#post-4539802</guid>
				<title>Image provenance</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-707543/scp-1793#post-4539802</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2020 04:11:03 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Voct</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>392303</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The Wayback Machine shows that this image has been on Rabbit.org <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20100802195005/http://www.rabbit.org/journal/1/making-a-houserabbit.html">since at least 2010</a>, three years before it was here. It may be older, but I see no need to pick through the wayback machine to figure out <em>how much</em> older.</p> <p>the phrases &quot;public domain&quot; and &quot;creative commons&quot; do not appear anywhere on rabbit.org; as such, I conclude that none of the photos on that site are suitably licensed for us.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
