						 <p>Carrots are crazy complicated biochemical objects. That stuff is <em>difficult</em>. The technology stuff is way way way way easier, but since they are advanced aliens, no-one is using that very often to they have to reconfigure their factories to produce it before it can be sent. Books and art and stuff can be appreciated by aliens too so that can be produced quickly.</p> 
